00:05:51,762 --> 00:05:52,660
Hello

18
00:05:53,064 --> 00:05:53,962
Hello

19
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,537
Hello

20
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:04,038
Hello

21
00:06:04,308 --> 00:06:05,206
Hello

22
00:06:05,776 --> 00:06:06,572
...I'm saying

23
00:06:07,211 --> 00:06:07,973
Yeah, Nikhil...

24
00:06:08,913 --> 00:06:12,178
one of our boys is an important comrade

25
00:06:12,783 --> 00:06:16,480
arrangements are to be made for his stay:
a shelter

26
00:06:17,288 --> 00:06:18,880
I believe staying at your place is best.

27
00:06:20,024 --> 00:06:20,724
Yes.

28
00:06:20,958 --> 00:06:23,392
It is not very safe where he is now...

29
00:07:08,173 --> 00:07:08,798
May I come in?...

30
00:07:09,708 --> 00:07:10,408
Who?...

31
00:07:10,743 --> 00:07:11,539
Come... come

32
00:07:13,145 --> 00:07:14,578
Got slightly delayed with serving your tea...

33
00:07:14,914 --> 00:07:16,074
Your clock isn't working.

34
00:07:17,416 --> 00:07:18,212
Isn't it?

35
00:07:22,988 --> 00:07:24,506
Yes, it's running.

36
00:07:25,007 --> 00:07:25,924
What?

37
00:07:25,925 --> 00:07:26,721
It's running...

38
00:07:28,193 --> 00:07:29,057
Meaning?

39
00:07:29,495 --> 00:07:31,395
It runs while flat and doesn't when it's
standing.

40
00:07:31,931 --> 00:07:32,556
Then how do I see the time?

41
00:07:32,765 --> 00:07:33,424
Like this.

42
00:07:35,367 --> 00:07:36,197
Funny.

43
00:07:37,937 --> 00:07:40,235
For me... it's not working even lying flat

44
00:07:43,676 --> 00:07:45,166
The tea is slightly strong today
isn't it...

45
00:07:45,311 --> 00:07:46,111
No... I prefer strong tea...

46
00:07:46,812 --> 00:07:48,404
Everybody in our house prefers strong tea...

47
00:07:49,648 --> 00:07:50,615
Let me arrange this...

48
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:51,850
Yeah.

49
00:07:52,585 --> 00:07:54,610
Biman will come tomorrow very early in the
morning

50
00:07:54,954 --> 00:07:56,046
and will take you somewhere else...

51
00:07:57,523 --> 00:07:58,751
Well, don't feel bad...

52
00:08:01,694 --> 00:08:04,162
Today here... tomorrow there... Nothing
fixed...

53
00:08:05,464 --> 00:08:07,159
Your mother doesn't like it at all

54
00:08:08,434 --> 00:08:10,664
I know... surely she asks you to come home

55
00:08:11,337 --> 00:08:12,037
Doesn't she?

56
00:08:15,774 --> 00:08:17,571
Have you a sister or a brother?

57
00:08:18,944 --> 00:08:21,504
You know, something terrible happened
in my school...

58
00:08:23,115 --> 00:08:25,481
Oh I forgot to wash your shirt...

59
00:08:26,418 --> 00:08:28,750
let me wash it now,
it'll be dry by tonight...

60
00:08:32,026 --> 00:08:32,726
Ready.

61
00:08:32,793 --> 00:08:33,817
I'm waiting for you...

62
00:08:34,662 --> 00:08:35,321
Would you go wearing this shirt?

63
00:08:35,830 --> 00:08:36,991
What's wrong?
- Are you going for action?

64
00:08:37,832 --> 00:08:39,429
What do you mean by action?
- I knew... that's why I made arrangements...

65
00:08:40,401 --> 00:08:42,160
What arrangements?
- Just see.

66
00:08:43,738 --> 00:08:44,901
Look.
- What's this?

67
00:08:45,006 --> 00:08:46,304
Shirt.
- What about it?

68
00:08:46,507 --> 00:08:48,041
You'll wear it.
- Why should I wear it?

69
00:08:48,309 --> 00:08:49,173
Do you know where we're going?

70
00:08:49,644 --> 00:08:50,611
Where? Wherever I go?

71
00:08:50,878 --> 00:08:52,345
You'll have to wear this
where you're going.

72
00:08:54,682 --> 00:08:58,648
These are bell bottoms.
- Biman, I've never worn these.

73
00:08:59,353 --> 00:09:00,786
You've never gone to that place either.

74
00:09:01,756 --> 00:09:04,122
You'll make me a Park streeter...

75
00:09:12,633 --> 00:09:14,601
What, you haven't shaved?
Shave.

76
00:09:39,194 --> 00:09:41,827
Whose flat?
- A lady's.

77
00:09:42,564 --> 00:09:43,926
Rich?
- No.

78
00:09:44,699 --> 00:09:46,064
Don't you have any other questions?

79
00:09:49,370 --> 00:09:50,394
Young or old?

80
00:09:50,738 --> 00:09:55,875
Don't know, never seen her, Nikhil's contact...
- Our person?

81
00:09:56,277 --> 00:10:01,139
Allows us to stay... Remember
the name, Shila Mitra.

82
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:04,810
You will see her after a couple of days.

83
00:10:06,488 --> 00:10:08,115
She is away now... Delhi...

84
00:10:10,125 --> 00:10:11,023
Will she return?...

85
00:10:11,326 --> 00:10:12,020
I'm told... after a couple of days...

86
00:10:12,794 --> 00:10:13,852
You've to stay alone for two days.

87
00:10:14,829 --> 00:10:15,454
Alone?...

88
00:10:16,397 --> 00:10:18,558
The lady lives alone?

89
00:10:21,970 --> 00:10:23,961
This is the key to paradise...

90
00:10:33,982 --> 00:10:34,682
Come.

91
00:10:46,628 --> 00:10:51,531
Wow!
Fantastic...

92
00:10:54,936 --> 00:10:58,394
8th floor means you're 9 storeyed.

93
00:11:00,008 --> 00:11:00,872
Decorated hell...

94
00:11:01,442 --> 00:11:04,202
What do you say?
- Hell.

95
00:11:06,247 --> 00:11:09,114
Any difference between jail
and this place?

96
00:11:11,352 --> 00:11:13,750
Oh! Money plant...

97
00:11:15,523 --> 00:11:18,591
Money on shaking... good luck

98
00:11:19,894 --> 00:11:26,399
Me, you, our landlady...
what do you say?

99
00:11:26,901 --> 00:11:30,200
Didn't you include our group?
The party... let me keep it inside...

100
00:11:30,672 --> 00:11:32,936
Biman... have you been here before?...

101
00:11:33,408 --> 00:11:34,108
Mad or what?

102
00:11:36,811 --> 00:11:39,211
Goddamn what a place... Superb.

103
00:11:40,248 --> 00:11:41,613
You said that there's no telephone...

104
00:11:44,352 --> 00:11:45,341
Hey... don't pick it up...

105
00:11:48,556 --> 00:11:51,855
Let it ring, what's that to you and me?...

106
00:11:56,864 --> 00:11:58,297
Can't say, may even be the C.I.A...

107
00:12:05,807 --> 00:12:06,507
Stop it.

108
00:12:15,785 --> 00:12:16,485
Give a cigarette.

109
00:12:20,556 --> 00:12:25,084
My cigarette stock is almost finished... could
you get me few packs of Charminar?

110
00:12:38,341 --> 00:12:39,035
Relieved.

111
00:12:42,078 --> 00:12:44,304
The lady gets up very early?
- How could you get up?

112
00:12:45,748 --> 00:12:47,147
Or else who could have called so early?

113
00:12:48,017 --> 00:12:49,746
Good... good for the health

114
00:12:52,255 --> 00:12:57,219
The time...
passing the time is very difficult...

115
00:12:59,328 --> 00:13:02,923
I'm thinking... I'll write an adventure story
about these details...

116
00:13:07,436 --> 00:13:09,562
What... Biman...

117
00:13:11,541 --> 00:13:12,701
This is a girl's room...

118
00:13:13,576 --> 00:13:14,372
I mean a lady's

119
00:13:15,077 --> 00:13:18,171
First class, very safe...
nobody will enter...

120
00:13:19,015 --> 00:13:22,109
...it will be trespass on entry...
We'll file a case.

121
00:13:22,685 --> 00:13:25,017
But these materials are Mrs Mitra's.
See what have you done?

122
00:13:25,121 --> 00:13:25,746
Please stop.

123
00:13:26,556 --> 00:13:29,491
You stay here... this is much safer.

124
00:13:30,893 --> 00:13:31,593
Okay.

125
00:13:33,062 --> 00:13:34,108
But the matter is...

126
00:13:34,109 --> 00:13:36,724
Listen, be careful,
till she comes back...

127
00:13:37,733 --> 00:13:38,859
That means I don't have to be careful when
she returns...

128
00:13:39,101 --> 00:13:40,934
Stay as safe as you can.
- I understand.

129
00:13:42,238 --> 00:13:44,365
Now I'm going... I've arranged everything
properly...

130
00:13:44,774 --> 00:13:47,872
There's the toilet... here's the key
- Key?

131
00:13:49,378 --> 00:13:50,510
Key... for the flat?
- Yes

132
00:13:51,314 --> 00:13:53,782
What can I do with the key of the flat?
I'm not going out for a stroll.

133
00:13:54,684 --> 00:13:55,343
Keep it with you...

134
00:13:56,085 --> 00:13:58,377
You'll be coming?
- Yeah... I'll be coming... okay

135
00:14:05,127 --> 00:14:06,185
Biman, listen.

136
00:14:12,969 --> 00:14:13,669
Biman.

137
00:14:14,537 --> 00:14:15,902
Who am I?

138
00:14:16,105 --> 00:14:20,872
Oh! Sorry... forgot to tell you.
You are Mrs Mitra's.

139
00:14:30,219 --> 00:14:31,743
Salaam sir... I'm the cleaner...

140
00:14:32,355 --> 00:14:33,515
I've come to check whether you've arrived

141
00:14:33,723 --> 00:14:36,123
Yeah... he's arrived... taking a bath inside

142
00:14:37,426 --> 00:14:39,401
Madam has asked me
to take care of you.

143
00:14:39,402 --> 00:14:42,796
I'll be downstairs always...
if you need me just call.

144
00:14:43,399 --> 00:14:44,099
Okay...

145
00:14:47,003 --> 00:14:47,993
Who?
- The cleaner...

146
00:14:52,408 --> 00:14:55,775
has come to take care as per madam's
instruction...

147
00:14:57,413 --> 00:15:01,110
You are madam's cousin...

148
00:15:02,518 --> 00:15:07,512
you live in Delhi... you've come here
for a visit...

149
00:15:10,059 --> 00:15:11,720
Come here for a visit.

150
00:15:16,098 --> 00:15:16,928
And Mr. Mitra?

151
00:15:17,366 --> 00:15:18,196
Let him go to hell...

152
00:16:35,078 --> 00:16:41,039
Yesterday in Dum Dum area north Calcutta
3 terrorists escaped from a police van...

153
00:16:42,219 --> 00:16:45,484
Immediately after this an intensive search
was started...

154
00:16:46,523 --> 00:16:49,712
It is reported that
though 2 out of the 3 escaped...

155
00:16:49,713 --> 00:16:51,722
They captured the other one...

156
00:16:54,364 --> 00:16:55,956
Would you get me some tea... strong.

157
00:17:02,239 --> 00:17:02,967
Does Nikhil know?

158
00:17:04,007 --> 00:17:05,167
He must by this time.

159
00:17:06,943 --> 00:17:08,001
The action was not correct.

160
00:17:08,779 --> 00:17:13,113
I took a great risk... it's only luck
that I wasn't caught...

161
00:17:15,218 --> 00:17:20,554
Mass copying has started in
various colleges in Calcutta...

162
00:17:20,657 --> 00:17:23,825
so that the V.C. of Calcutta
University Satyendranath Sen

163
00:17:23,826 --> 00:17:26,994
has met in Darbhanga Hall with the
principals of all colleges...

164
00:17:27,998 --> 00:17:32,560
Apart from other things the disease
of bad habits that...

165
00:17:35,105 --> 00:17:39,667
Escaped, got caught, escaped again...

166
00:17:42,045 --> 00:17:44,411
So what now?

167
00:17:46,249 --> 00:17:46,874
What?

168
00:17:48,185 --> 00:17:49,015
You'll stay absconding...

169
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:55,020
I'll remain a fugitive... only a fugitive,
nothing else...

170
00:17:57,561 --> 00:17:58,721
...'sports news'

171
00:17:59,396 --> 00:18:01,591
That day I met your father on the streets...

172
00:18:02,966 --> 00:18:04,900
I was returning home from the office
after marketing...

173
00:18:06,536 --> 00:18:13,840
He talked about this and that, talked about
many things but never once asked about you.

174
00:18:14,845 --> 00:18:18,804
Not even once. I think he is very angry
with you.

175
00:18:19,783 --> 00:18:22,547
Very much... Since you're a revolutionary.

176
00:18:31,027 --> 00:18:35,054
But you said once your father was in a
terrorist party...

177
00:18:36,366 --> 00:18:38,129
was in prison during British Rule.

178
00:18:52,716 --> 00:18:55,708
Then he was greatly involved
in the movement of '42...

179
00:18:56,853 --> 00:19:00,152
I don't know how people changed so much.

180
00:19:12,369 --> 00:19:15,258
He would probably say the
nation has become independent

181
00:19:15,259 --> 00:19:16,703
and there are lots of changes.

182
00:19:17,774 --> 00:19:19,833
But what has happened?

183
00:19:21,211 --> 00:19:29,211
Inclub zindabad...

184
00:21:32,537 --> 00:21:34,801
Bobby Bobby...

185
00:21:44,916 --> 00:21:45,905
Come Bobby

186
00:21:46,418 --> 00:21:48,716
I said don't.

187
00:22:15,547 --> 00:22:17,515
You know... always there's fear...

188
00:22:18,149 --> 00:22:20,117
Yeah fear... even in a lift.

189
00:22:20,985 --> 00:22:21,679
How?

190
00:22:22,087 --> 00:22:23,578
Believe me... as many
people are in the house

191
00:22:23,579 --> 00:22:24,647
...the number of dogs are not less

192
00:22:25,457 --> 00:22:26,775
Chased...

193
00:22:26,776 --> 00:22:30,122
Yeah, you smelled of revolution?

194
00:22:30,228 --> 00:22:33,220
Not at all, comrade of bread and curry...
let me put it away...

195
00:22:34,165 --> 00:22:40,502
Hey Biman... this is too much...
there was no need for this.

196
00:22:40,638 --> 00:22:45,632
So... you wouldn't have eaten
anything... fasting?

197
00:22:47,145 --> 00:22:47,941
Take a look.

198
00:22:50,815 --> 00:22:51,907
Wow!

199
00:22:52,617 --> 00:22:53,413
Oh!

200
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:56,981
With all the food that is here,
I can feed you for 2 days...

201
00:22:58,056 --> 00:23:01,548
and here there's gas, a stove etc... will
you eat?

202
00:23:01,826 --> 00:23:04,090
For now you eat this... I'm going

203
00:23:05,497 --> 00:23:06,794
What's the hurry with you?

204
00:23:06,898 --> 00:23:08,490
Oh! I've brought cigarettes for you

205
00:23:09,467 --> 00:23:10,263
4 packs of Charminar...

206
00:23:10,835 --> 00:23:11,563
Relieved

207
00:23:13,438 --> 00:23:16,498
Here's a match box... okay I'm going

208
00:23:17,375 --> 00:23:18,364
Hey Biman...

209
00:23:19,411 --> 00:23:23,040
you are moving about so much,
be careful...

210
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,873
Karim

211
00:25:58,201 --> 00:25:59,005
Karim

212
00:26:01,773 --> 00:26:05,002
Bishey...

213
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:18,815
Only sleeping... do you know how late it is?

214
00:26:20,205 --> 00:26:22,318
Prepare the tea, get up...

215
00:26:58,552 --> 00:26:59,528
How many spoonfuls?

216
00:27:00,741 --> 00:27:01,373
Eh...

217
00:27:02,730 --> 00:27:03,637
...one & a half

218
00:28:21,809 --> 00:28:23,314
Father you leave... I'll stay here...

219
00:28:25,853 --> 00:28:27,127
What'll you do by being here?

220
00:28:27,908 --> 00:28:30,021
You'll be late for the office...
go for a bath... I'll stay here.

221
00:28:30,637 --> 00:28:36,470
You haven't forgotten that I must go
to the office and arrange for your food...

222
00:28:36,471 --> 00:28:38,048
You still remember it...

223
00:28:40,442 --> 00:28:44,142
You go. There's nothing to be done here
except removing the pulse from the oven...

224
00:28:51,731 --> 00:28:52,730
How are you, mother?

225
00:28:54,259 --> 00:28:55,637
Well.

226
00:28:56,752 --> 00:28:59,244
Who went to bring the ration today?

227
00:29:00,964 --> 00:29:06,387
Who else except for him... why?

228
00:29:06,463 --> 00:29:10,463
No... I found father's mood is a bit off...
that's why.

229
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:20,970
Look. The milk is here. It's hot...
drink it when it gets cool...

230
00:29:27,950 --> 00:29:30,511
Huh!

231
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:34,157
Where is Biru? Not in the house.

232
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,000
No.

233
00:29:35,120 --> 00:29:37,200
He went out first thing in the morning.

234
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:39,000
Oh... he is having his class exams.

235
00:30:07,429 --> 00:30:12,473
We too have worked for the country... have
gone to prison...

236
00:30:13,158 --> 00:30:17,334
our concern for the betterment of the
country is no less than anyone else's...

237
00:30:17,335 --> 00:30:20,535
I find the young boys have
become so irresponsible nowadays.

238
00:30:20,942 --> 00:30:21,642
Listen, father...

239
00:30:22,862 --> 00:30:23,839
I know... I know...

240
00:30:24,312 --> 00:30:28,853
I won't be able to win a verbal battle
with you... you have become learned...

241
00:30:28,854 --> 00:30:32,929
reading a few books of the party
makes you think you've become very wise

242
00:30:34,454 --> 00:30:39,497
you just make a shower of words... we too
knew about the revolutionaries,

243
00:30:40,755 --> 00:30:44,730
talked about revolution... We too
read the works of Lenin.

244
00:30:45,944 --> 00:30:47,463
Where were you then...

245
00:30:47,464 --> 00:30:52,573
your leaders were drowsing in the
dark... used to take opium, I understand

246
00:30:53,560 --> 00:30:55,041
...opium...

247
00:30:55,548 --> 00:30:58,327
Listen father... what you
don't know or don't understand

248
00:30:58,328 --> 00:30:59,546
about those things...
like a fool.

249
00:31:07,562 --> 00:31:08,263
So...

250
00:31:09,584 --> 00:31:10,250
why did you stop?

251
00:31:11,404 --> 00:31:12,105
Say it.

252
00:31:16,897 --> 00:31:19,113
Come eat... you are going to be late for
the office

253
00:31:19,862 --> 00:31:23,361
Stop... no one needs to do
anything for me...

254
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:37,000
Just see these boys nowadays... they
can say things that they're not supposed to

255
00:31:37,192 --> 00:31:42,236
will say whatever they like... wonderful...
I'll be late for the office.

256
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:46,186
Nobody will have to remind me about my
responsibility...

257
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:49,000
Ask you to go... go eat...

258
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,900
