607
01:04:40,289 --> 01:04:42,053
but this is not enough of a change...

608
01:04:42,054 --> 01:04:45,907
because the main thing is the
oppressive social conditions...

609
01:04:46,253 --> 01:04:49,044
Here if the social structure is not changed,
the freedom of women is doubtful...

610
01:04:50,027 --> 01:04:55,953
The conditions are so intertwined that

611
01:04:55,954 --> 01:05:01,879
