771
01:21:46,430 --> 01:21:47,740
that's my personal matter...

772
01:21:49,428 --> 01:21:51,610
yeah... I'm not bound to give an explanation
for this.

773
01:21:53,741 --> 01:21:55,993
No... no!

774
01:22:04,457 --> 01:22:05,560
What did Nikhil say?

775
01:22:07,725 --> 01:22:10,850
Probably I can't stay in this house
anymore.

776
01:22:12,544 --> 01:22:14,219
Why?
- That only Nikhil knows...

777
01:22:14,869 --> 01:22:15,846
and Biman.

778
01:22:39,069 --> 01:22:39,770
Come in.

779
01:22:43,180 --> 01:22:44,087
Sit.

780
01:22:46,684 --> 01:22:48,603
What's your news? It's been so long.

781
01:22:48,875 --> 01:22:50,862
The key to your flat...
I'll not be needing it anymore

782
01:23:07,104 --> 01:23:08,011
Would you have tea or coffee?

783
01:23:08,216 --> 01:23:09,089
I'm in a hurry.

784
01:23:10,305 --> 01:23:12,522
Wait for 5 minutes...
I've finished my work...

785
01:23:13,203 --> 01:23:14,684
we will go together, yeah.

786
01:23:14,888 --> 01:23:17,312
No... today I'm in a hurry... okay?

787
01:23:30,028 --> 01:23:33,757
There's a saying in Bengali:
a dilemma everywhere...

788
01:23:33,758 --> 01:23:36,290
my condition is more or less like that.

789
01:23:40,542 --> 01:23:41,449
I was saying...

790
01:23:43,238 --> 01:23:44,340
was saying

791
01:23:46,406 --> 01:23:47,404
Here I've no problem...

792
01:23:49,134 --> 01:23:49,904
you can stay here.

793
01:23:53,548 --> 01:23:54,961
No... I can't

794
01:23:57,154 --> 01:23:57,819
Why?

795
01:23:59,648 --> 01:24:06,013
You thought everything is finished...
now only comfort and rest...

796
01:24:10,936 --> 01:24:12,176
But I've not said this to you.

797
01:24:13,968 --> 01:24:14,772
You know...

798
01:24:17,136 --> 01:24:21,169
the time it takes to build a party,
it is the same when leaving.

799
01:24:22,932 --> 01:24:25,758
But the party wants you...

800
01:24:26,875 --> 01:24:27,540
Look...

801
01:24:28,997 --> 01:24:31,996
the party is nobody's personal property.

802
01:24:33,782 --> 01:24:37,550
You've got to fight inside and outside.

803
01:24:38,980 --> 01:24:39,956
You are alone.

804
01:24:41,002 --> 01:24:41,771
At present.

805
01:24:43,192 --> 01:24:44,191
Biman will not come to this house anymore.

806
01:24:48,213 --> 01:24:49,051
I know...

807
01:24:51,415 --> 01:24:53,402
...once I too was like Biman...

808
01:24:55,020 --> 01:24:56,191
didn't know how to question...

809
01:24:57,917 --> 01:25:05,488
cannon fodder without questions, without
thought.

810
01:25:47,451 --> 01:25:49,633
Where is Sumit? I need Sumit very badly...

811
01:25:52,641 --> 01:25:54,019
the condition of Aunty is very bad...

812
01:25:54,662 --> 01:25:57,960
your mother... your brother came to my
house...

813
01:25:59,043 --> 01:26:04,868
Wants to see you at once... do what you think
best... I'm going...

814
01:24:38,980 --> 01:24:39,956
You are alone.

815
01:24:41,002 --> 01:24:41,771
At present.

816
01:24:43,192 --> 01:24:44,191
Biman will not come to this house anymore.

817
01:24:48,213 --> 01:24:49,051
I know...

818
01:24:51,415 --> 01:24:53,402
...once I too was like Biman...

819
01:24:55,020 --> 01:24:56,191
didn't know how to question...

820
01:24:57,917 --> 01:25:05,488
cannon fodder without question, without
thought.

821
01:25:47,451 --> 01:25:49,633
Where is Sumit? I need Sumit very badly...

822
01:25:52,641 --> 01:25:54,019
the condition of Aunty is very bad...

823
01:25:54,662 --> 01:25:57,960
your mother... your brother came to my
house...

824
01:25:59,043 --> 01:26:04,868
Wants to see you once... do what you think
best... I'm going...

825
01:26:08,856 --> 01:26:09,959
Biman!

826
01:26:17,550 --> 01:26:18,549
Now what will you do?

827
01:26:20,987 --> 01:26:21,859
What's the time?

828
01:26:22,873 --> 01:26:23,677
It's about 9

829
01:26:23,884 --> 01:26:24,591
Oh!

830
01:26:26,682 --> 01:26:28,864
I can drop you there?

831
01:26:40,059 --> 01:26:42,678
Okay... stop here... I'll get out...

832
01:26:43,462 --> 01:26:44,875
it won't be prudent to go any further.

833
01:26:45,586 --> 01:26:48,377
You'd better go...

834
01:26:49,123 --> 01:26:51,304
Please ring me and inform me how she is.
- I'll try...

835
01:26:51,718 --> 01:26:53,291
Do you know my number?
- Yes

836
01:26:53,706 --> 01:26:54,476
I will wait...

837
01:26:55,425 --> 01:26:58,182
You should leave. It won't be safe for you
to stay here alone.

838
01:27:30,334 --> 01:27:32,414
Who? Who?

839
01:27:32,544 --> 01:27:33,348
You?

840
01:27:35,644 --> 01:27:36,747
Could have come a bit earlier...

841
01:27:38,508 --> 01:27:39,921
since you finally came...

842
01:27:43,361 --> 01:27:45,750
yeah, she wanted to see you.

843
01:27:48,044 --> 01:27:48,848
Go

844
01:27:51,650 --> 01:27:52,454
Go

845
01:28:34,006 --> 01:28:34,879
Biru

846
01:28:37,308 --> 01:28:38,112
Biru

847
01:28:40,409 --> 01:28:41,213
Biru

848
01:28:51,326 --> 01:28:54,083
Why didn't come a bit earlier... you could
have seen her alive.

849
01:29:03,693 --> 01:29:07,725
Biru, when did you inform Biman?

850
01:29:08,444 --> 01:29:11,305
You were informed... who gave the message?

851
01:29:33,009 --> 01:29:33,812
Listen.

852
01:29:35,064 --> 01:29:35,729
Me.

853
01:29:36,648 --> 01:29:40,140
I want to talk to you... come.

854
01:29:46,521 --> 01:29:48,566
Hello, how are you dear?

855
01:29:49,419 --> 01:29:50,154
Well

856
01:29:53,968 --> 01:29:54,675
Sit

857
01:29:56,461 --> 01:29:58,977
Please go away. I'll talk for some time.

858
01:30:01,280 --> 01:30:04,370
That you've come is very good...

859
01:30:06,469 --> 01:30:09,732
You are the elder son... you have
responsibilities.

860
01:30:10,951 --> 01:30:16,569
They have come, all these people..
they are all aware.

861
01:30:18,196 --> 01:30:23,883
So I was saying it won't be right for you
to stay here...

862
01:30:27,698 --> 01:30:30,489
so I was saying don't worry about me...

863
01:30:32,483 --> 01:30:37,081
they are here... somehow they'll manage
the necessary work

864
01:30:37,082 --> 01:30:39,985
and Biru will do the last rites.

865
01:30:42,793 --> 01:30:44,907
You'd better go before more people are aware.

866
01:30:54,621 --> 01:30:57,413
Father, please be careful.

867
01:30:58,327 --> 01:30:59,304
I'll be alright...

868
01:31:00,889 --> 01:31:05,128
and Biru's job... I believe
he'll get it... but...

869
01:31:06,449 --> 01:31:09,240
I'm going... I'm going.

870
01:31:10,021 --> 01:31:10,825
Okay.

871
01:31:18,242 --> 01:31:19,149
Well.

872
01:31:20,062 --> 01:31:21,406
Mother talked about me?

873
01:31:22,455 --> 01:31:23,155
Yeah.

874
01:31:26,027 --> 01:31:27,738
I haven't yet said one thing to you.

875
01:31:29,329 --> 01:31:30,305
I didn't tell your mother...

876
01:31:31,553 --> 01:31:32,758
because of what would happen if I told her...

877
01:31:33,844 --> 01:31:38,451
It wouldn't do her any good...
let the rest of her days be peaceful.

878
01:31:40,348 --> 01:31:41,519
7 days ago...

879
01:31:42,975 --> 01:31:46,341
the manager of our office called me
into his room...

880
01:31:47,221 --> 01:31:50,747
only me... called many others...

881
01:31:52,478 --> 01:31:59,280
and gave me a printed paper bond
I won't be able to strike gold with.

882
01:32:01,070 --> 01:32:05,678
but I'm telling you...
I haven't signed that bond.

883
01:32:09,798 --> 01:32:12,693
Go... to war.

884
01:32:43,730 --> 01:32:48,739
FOOT SOLDIER.
